did.unittitle: Rockefeller University records, Dean of Graduate Studies, Series 1

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Records more than 25 years old are open for research with select materials restricted as noted. Brittle or damaged items are available at the discretion of RAC.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Information regarding the Rockefeller Archive Center's preferred elements and forms of citation can be found at http://www.rockarch.org/research/citations.php

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Includes, but not necessarily limited to, files regarding course and seminar announcements and evaluations, Academic Committee records, budgets, faculty reports, lectures, student lectures, examinations, lab demonstrations, convocations, fellowships, scholarships and aid, summer programs, requisitions, expenses and surveys.

otherfindaid.head: Other Finding Aids
otherfindaid.p: For Dean of Graduate Studies records that are currently open for scholarly reseach see:

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Minimal processing. Some materials remain in original housing.
